{"tid":1475645,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每日四點鐘記者會都聽到厭？不如試下","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:29:52.000Z","uid":264614,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d2038dc622c38ed81f65079635b29d09a078dac","tid":1475645,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"代朋友Post<br />\n<br />\n我有一條橋，如果個四點鐘 警察記者招待會 警察開始學大陸個套 專問親中記者問題 唔比機會其他人搶咪 就算答又答非所問遊花園既話，記者可以咁做：<br />\n<br />\n第一，叫東方 港台 成報 蘋果記者成立一個暫時既聯盟，集體杯葛個記者招待會，然後係各自報紙度集中將大家既問題 用頭條、或者是但一版啦，整一個清單出黎，向警察書面發問，反正在場都唔會答。<br />\n<br />\n就算去記者招待會都淨係派一個代表 去 唔好出聲。<br />\n<br />\n第二日要出報紙時，用梁振英式腔調幫個幫個記者招待會做總結，例如「今日警察記招 第一間發問的機構是大公報、第二間是文匯報....清單上問題暫時一條都仍未作答」。"},{"pid":"8c9a90ee3dfc0f4b59adc94808665d5a79fdfacb","tid":1475645,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:44.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"fe7b9b26322abf51f14772867939c5ca55665fa7","tid":1475645,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b149cb4cf97e163dedf2b210d7a67627b2a75d09","tid":1475645,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bce4ef4bb63355fc893259ee730f2b4375d9848e","tid":1475645,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a0fc01737aedf0315ff92170d44763aa77fb15d","tid":1475645,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:23:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"796570a29a69173cfd7eb489c264e02b10917e6d","tid":1475645,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a7bfb003c2043d2303743debd2c529cb5a36882","tid":1475645,"uid":158026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n一直都係咁諗"},{"pid":"736dac016de9cba9cf78e9a89e6356516acc641b","tid":1475645,"uid":241244,"like":